	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Jun 26th 4:16 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>This bug is due to lag, and hitting mend when your PC and the server are out of sync.&nbsp;&nbsp;It actually used to be quite a bit worse (they put in a fix for it) -- now, I find it only happens rarely.<br><br>If you have been experiencing lag, especially if this bug has happened during a session , try waiting a few seconds before hitting mend.  Also, make sure the connection monitor shows 0% lag.  This will usually take care of the problem.<br><br>Note that if you zone after getting this bug, mend will refresh upon zoning, and you will NOT have to wait for a full cycle to try again.<br>&nbsp;<br>Osano<br>Level 44 Human Monk<br>Tholuxe-Paells</td></tr>
