	   <tr><td colspan=2>Fish fillets. <br><br>Possibly one of the cheapest and easiest trade skills to get up, and the cost to profit ratio is probably the best. <br><br>Check out eqtraders.com for baking recipes, and the such. Get your skill up to around 135 (took me about two hours,) and then just make tons of fish fillets. <br><br>It's boring, but it's good money, especially around level 18 where the loot is not so good. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
