	   <tr><td colspan=2>I didnt put all my input in that post, I admit.&nbsp;&nbsp;You are right, when fighting Casters (something I only do in groups, of course) I "switch to the machine guns" and use FB/CoT combo.  For these levels, I will keep the 2HB for pure high damage, and against Damage Shields, and I'm sure I will switch to the 1HB's later as the bonuses for the primary hand weapon increase.  Right now, I'm still doing Giants in FM, and I can drop a Hillock fast with the 2HB, a Tump Moderately so with 1HB's.  I group, there are normally 3 of us monks, and we share our weapons with each other to keep our skills maxed.  One of us has THE Tunic, and we share it at the end of a fight to keep the down time minimized if we dont have the benefit of a healer available.  Good to be in a decent guild where you can share an item worth 40k pp's and not have to think twice about worrying.  :) <br><br>Jazzwind<br>31 Monk<br>Crew<br>Rodcet Nife<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
